Class EmailPasswordAuthenticationData

java.lang.Object
  com.netflix.msl.userauth.UserAuthenticationData
      com.netflix.msl.userauth.EmailPasswordAuthenticationData

public class EmailPasswordAuthenticationData
extends UserAuthenticationData

Email/password-based user authentication data.

{ "#mandatory" : [ "email", "password" ], "email" : "string", "password" : "string" } where:

  • email is the user email address
  • password is the user password
